graph TD
    A[Trained model weights] --> B[Rank weights by absolute value]
    B --> C[Zero out smallest-magnitude weights first]
    C --> D{Pruning granularity}
    D -->|Unstructured| E[Individual weights zeroed: max sparsity, needs sparse kernels]
    D -->|Structured| F[Whole neurons or channels removed: real speedup on dense hardware]
    E --> G[Sparser and smaller model]
    F --> G
    G --> H{Accuracy check}
    H -->|Accuracy drop recoverable| I[Fine-tune to recover accuracy]
    I --> B
    H -->|Sparsity too high: accuracy falls off a cliff| J[Stop: keep last good checkpoint]
